title: Jujutsu Kaisen
description: Yuuji, a student at Sugisawa Town #3 High School, happens to be ultra-talented at track and field… But since he has no interest in running around in circles, he’s happy as a clam being a member of the Occult Research Club! Although he only joined up for kicks, things start to get serious when an actual spirit shows up at the school.
author: Gege Akutami
